ility (spell save DC 11): Augury, Find Familiar, Identify, Locate Object, Scrying, or Unseen Servant. The hag must finish a Long Rest before using this trait to cast that spell again.", "attackBonus": 0, "damageDice": "", "damageBonus": 0, "damageType": "", "category": "", "normalRange": 0, "longRange": 0, "saveAbility": "", "saveAbilityLabel": "", "saveDC": 0, "rangeSquares": 0, "multiattackCount": 0, "healAmount": 0}, {"name": "Mimicry", "desc": "Mimicry. The hag can mimic animal sounds and humanoid voices. A creature that hears the sounds can tell they are imitations only with a successful DC 14 Wisdom (Insight) check.", "attackBonus": 0, "damageDice": "", "damageBonus": 0, "damageType": "", "category": "", "normalRange": 0, "longRange": 0, "saveAbility": "", "saveAbilityLabel": "", "saveDC": 0, "rangeSquares": 0, "multiattackCount": 0, "healAmount": 0}]', legendary_actions_json = NULL, reactions_json = NULL WHERE name = 'Green Hag';
